metadata.name: Quest
metadata.description:
This artwork is called Quest. The meaning behind this is the character is looking or searching for something that is lost for a while. I think it is a part of every persons life, something is lost and we are always looking for it in our life. The darkish purple theme is one of my favorite color schemes.

The Process of Quest is available on : www.twitter.com/classypaints.

Thank you :))
